<doc id="581016" wikidata="Q7102865" url="?curid=581016" title="Orissi">
<text>Orissi, also spelled Odissi ( &quot;oṛiśī&quot;) is an adjectival form of Odisha. It may refer to:
*Odissi dance, the classical dance of Odisha
*Orissi music, the classical music of Odisha
*other aspects of Orissi culture
*a person from Odisha</text><links>
